description:
This dataset includes Multiple Sequence Alignments (MSAs): 

  CASP15 Protein Dataset : MSAs were created for 93 protein targets using the AlphaFold 2.3 code.&nbsp; 
  rMSA RNA Dataset : MSAs were generated for 361 RNA targets utilizing the rMSA pipeline.&nbsp;

